    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Chop the<strong> sweet potatoes </strong>(skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Cut the<strong> yellow pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>in half, deseed (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into medium-sized chunks</p><p>Peel and cut the<strong> red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into wedges</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1657543378390-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
