      "instruction": "<p>After the initial 12-15 min, remove the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> from the oven and top with the<strong> cherry tomatoes</strong></p><p>Return the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> to the oven and cook for a final 10-12 min or until the tomatoes have softened and are starting to brown – this is your <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>patatas bravas traybake</strong></p>",
